{"article_id":"yymTDD2HEykpSl2D","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump is following through with one of the first pledges","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"he made a year and a half ago","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"when he announced his long-shot bid for the White House","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"-- directing federal resources toward building a wall along the southern border .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"But the reality","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"of building the wall","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"could be more difficult","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"than the rallying cries would suggest .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"The length of the wall , when construction will begin , how much it will cost","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"and who will pay for it remain fundamental questions .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"There is also ongoing debate about the feasibility of the structure and the need for it in the first place .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Trump 's push for a wall dates back to the day in June 2015","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"when he announced his campaign","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"and promised to `` build a great , great wall on our southern border ''","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Mexico would pay .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"His effort","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"to turn those words into reality","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"is expected to be formally announced Wednesday","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"and is among several immigration-related actions","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"anticipated in a multi-day rollout from the new administration .","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Trump pledges","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"to build a wall","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Trump pledges","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to build a wall","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"00:50","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Since he first made the pledge ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"walling off our neighbors to the south became an oft-repeated promise and rallying cry , both for the candidate and his supporters .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Chants of `` build that wall '' thundered through arenas and convention halls .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"In at least one instance , Trump himself led the cheer .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Building `` an impenetrable physical wall on the southern border , on day one '' is listed as item No . 1 on his `` 10 Point Plan","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"to Put America First . ''","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"At the first press briefing of the new administration Monday , one of the first questions to White House Press Secretary Sean Spicer was about the wall .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"Spicer said","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"the administration was working with agency heads and Congress","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"to move forward on the project .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"He offered no further details .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Not everyone is as enthusiastic as the President about building a wall ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"including the man","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"whose job","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"it was to secure the U.S. border for the past three years .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"`` I do n't see any efficacy","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"in building a wall across the border , ''","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"said Gil Kerlikowske ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"who until last week served as Commissioner of Customs and Border Protection under former President Barack Obama .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"`` The border and migration issues are just unbelievably complex , ''","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Kerlikowske said in an interview with CNN .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"`` And a simple answer to a complex problem is most assuredly the wrong answer . ''","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Kerlikowske said","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"the rugged terrain in the Arizona desert and the shifting Rio Grande River in Texas ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"which routinely changes depth and even direction ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"both represent natural obstacles","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"to building a border wall .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Some of the land along the border in the Rio Grande Valley is privately owned ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"representing another challenge ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Kerlikowske also noted","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that the vast majority of people","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"trying to enter the US","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"are actually showing up at border entry points","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"and seeking asylum","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"or turning themselves in .","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"Most are not trying to scale the fence in the dark of night ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Even if a wall was built ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"it would require a significant hiring increase","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"to have enough agents","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"to monitor the wall .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"That would be no easy feat for an agency","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that is currently 1,200 employees below full strength .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Kerlikowske said","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"that , in addition to some 700 miles of fencing , the border is currently patrolled by agents on foot , bikes , motorcycles , ATVs and horseback .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"There 's also an air wing , unmanned predator drones , ground sensors , infrared video and tower-mounted video with a range of 25 miles .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"`` It 's all preferable to a wall , ''","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Kerlikowske said .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"`` Unless you monitor that wall . ''","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"On the campaign trail , Trump told a crowd of supporters in Anaheim , California , in May","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"that he 'd reached out to leaders in the union","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"representing Border Patrol agents","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"and asked","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"whether a wall was truly needed .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"`` Mr. Trump , It 's absolutely vital , '' came the reply ,","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"he told the crowd .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"`` It 's an absolutely important tool .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Maybe our most important tool","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"to stop what 's going on . ''","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"`` We 're going to build the wall .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"We have no choice . ''","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"At the point , the crowd began chanting ,","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"`` build that wall . ''","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Trump joined in from the podium .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"The National Border Patrol Council , the union","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"representing Border Patrol agents ,","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"endorsed Trump for President","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"-- marking the first time","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"the group had taken such an action .","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"Brandon Judd , president of the council , said in a recent interview with CNN ,","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"that Trump was `` by far the best on border security ''","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"when compared with other candidates .","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"Judd said","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"he did n't reach that decision","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"based on his pledge","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"to build a wall .","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"He said","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"his group favored `` barriers in strategic locations . ''","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"But , importantly , he did n't say","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"those barriers had to come in the form of a wall","depth":16},{"id":112,"text":"as Trump is suggesting .","depth":16},{"id":113,"text":"He called the double fencing along the border in the San Diego area `` insanely effective . ''","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"Judd ,","depth":17},{"id":115,"text":"who said","depth":18},{"id":116,"text":"he met with Trump and his transition team ,","depth":18},{"id":117,"text":"argued","depth":16},{"id":118,"text":"such fencing allows agents to confront people on the US side of the border","depth":16},{"id":119,"text":"while they still have a fence in front of them","depth":17},{"id":120,"text":"to slow their progress .","depth":17},{"id":121,"text":"`` He was very much willing to listen to our perspective , ''","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"Judd said .","depth":15},{"id":123,"text":"`` It was ,","depth":16},{"id":124,"text":"you know :","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"' I did n't realize that ' .","depth":16},{"id":126,"text":"And 'that 's good to know ' . ''","depth":16},{"id":127,"text":"Trump would then turn to an aide ,","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"Judd recounted ,","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"and say :","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"`` Hey , get on this .","depth":17},{"id":131,"text":"Get back with me .","depth":17},{"id":132,"text":"I need to know more about this . ''","depth":16},{"id":133,"text":"Judd said","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"he was confident","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"his group 's views were being taken into consideration .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"`` If you look at the areas","depth":15},{"id":137,"text":"they 're currently surveying","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"--","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"if you look at what the talk is ,","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"a lot of that is coming from us , ''","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"`` They absolutely 100 % are in the process","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"of implementing things","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"we suggested . ''","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"Judd said","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"he signed a non-disclosure agreement","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"that prohibited him from going into detail about planned construction .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"Shawn Moran , vice president of the Border Patrol union , said","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"he thinks","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"most people would be surprised to learn","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"that it 's possible to drive for 30 minutes in some Border Patrol sectors","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"and not encounter agents on patrol .","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"a lot of Americans think","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"you 're going to see agents in towers every hundred yards , ''","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"Moran said .","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"`` That does n't exist . ''","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"one instance","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"in which a wall may have made a difference","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"was in the 2009 slaying of Border Patrol Agent Robert Rosas .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"Rosas was shot to death by assailants","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"who crawled under fencing near the eastern San Diego County town of Campo .","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"The US-Mexico border is approximately 2,000 miles long ,","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"running from San Diego to Brownsville , Texas .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"Trump initially said","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"he wanted to wall off the entire border ,","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"but has since said","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"that 1,000 miles may do .","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"He has offered few details on the wall","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"since being elected president .","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"But speaking at a news conference earlier this month ,","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"he reiterated his pledge ,","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"referring to the border as `` an open sieve . ''","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"He made construction sound imminent .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"`` Mike Pence is leading an effort","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"to get final approvals through various agencies and through Congress","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"for the wall to begin , ''","depth":14},{"id":179,"text":"he told reporters on Jan. 11 .","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"CNN reported earlier this month","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"that Trump transition team officials had been in discussions with the US Army Corps of Engineers and the Interior Department","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"to begin planning a wall ,","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"including how certain environmental laws could come into play .","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"`` It seems clear they were trying to size up the environmental laws","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"that may be obstacles","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"to building the wall , ''","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"said one U.S. official familiar with the inquiry .","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"A review of Trump 's statements on the campaign trail offers a glimpse of what he envisions","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"-- or did at the time .","depth":7},{"id":190,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"his wall would be solid , strong and `` probably 35 to 40 feet up in the air . ''","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"`` It will actually look good , ''","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"he added .","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"`` You know ,","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"as good as a wall is going to look . ''","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"The dimensions of the border barricade grew","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"when former Mexican President Vicente Fox insisted","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"his country would never pay for it .","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"`` It just got 10 feet taller , ''","depth":10},{"id":200,"text":"Trump told CNN 's Wolf Blitzer last year .","depth":10},{"id":201,"text":"When then-Republican presidential contender Jeb Bush referred to the proposed wall as a fence in August of 2015 ,","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"Trump took to Twitter","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"to correct him :","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"`` It 's not a fence , Jeb ,","depth":13},{"id":205,"text":"it 's a WALL , ''","depth":13},{"id":206,"text":"Trump tweeted ,","depth":12},{"id":207,"text":"`` and there 's a BIG difference ! ''","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"In an interview with MSNBC in February , then-candidate Trump said","depth":10},{"id":209,"text":"he 'd priced out the project at about $ 8 billion .","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"Later that month , he told Fox News ' Sean Hannity","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"the cost would be $ 10 billion .","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"`` It 's going to be a very terrific wall , ''","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"Trump said .","depth":13},{"id":214,"text":"`` $ 10 billion is not bad . ''","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"Hannity asked Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"whose name is synonymous with his brand as a builder and hotelier","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"whether the name Trump will be on the wall .","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":435,"left":0,"right":434,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":434,"left":238,"right":433,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":233,"right":237,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":228,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":221,"right":227,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":221,"left":220,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":1,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":224,"right":226,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":222,"right":223,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":222,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":226,"left":225,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":225,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":232,"left":12,"right":231,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":13,"right":230,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":230,"left":14,"right":229,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":229,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":237,"left":235,"right":236,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":235,"left":234,"right":19,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":234,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":433,"left":251,"right":432,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":251,"left":245,"right":250,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":245,"left":240,"right":244,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":22,"right":239,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":239,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":25,"right":243,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":243,"left":242,"right":29,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":26,"right":241,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":241,"left":27,"right":28,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":248,"right":249,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":246,"right":247,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":30,"right":31,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":247,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":249,"left":34,"right":35,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":432,"left":295,"right":431,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":295,"left":255,"right":294,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":36,"right":254,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":254,"left":253,"right":40,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":37,"right":252,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":252,"left":38,"right":39,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":281,"right":293,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":281,"left":265,"right":280,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":258,"right":264,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":41,"right":257,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":42,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":261,"right":263,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":259,"right":260,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":45,"right":46,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":262,"right":51,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":262,"left":49,"right":50,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":272,"right":279,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":272,"left":269,"right":271,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":52,"right":268,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":268,"left":266,"right":267,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":266,"left":53,"right":54,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":55,"right":56,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":270,"right":59,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":57,"right":58,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":277,"right":278,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":60,"right":276,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":276,"left":273,"right":275,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":273,"left":61,"right":62,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":63,"right":274,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":274,"left":64,"right":65,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":278,"left":66,"right":67,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":287,"right":292,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":287,"left":285,"right":286,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":282,"right":284,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":282,"left":68,"right":69,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":70,"right":283,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":71,"right":72,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":73,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":289,"right":291,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":288,"right":77,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":291,"left":290,"right":80,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":78,"right":79,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":431,"left":401,"right":430,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":401,"left":361,"right":400,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":361,"left":309,"right":360,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":309,"left":299,"right":308,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":299,"left":81,"right":298,"relation":"